(26, '<div class=\"post-text\" itemprop=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.3; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 660px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\">Principles to keep in mind if you want your applications to be secure:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Never trust any input!</strong></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/library/l-sp2.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">Validate input</a>&nbsp;from all untrusted sources - use whitelists not blacklists</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Plan for security from the start - it\'s not something you can bolt on at the end</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Keep it simple - complexity increases the likelihood of security holes</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Keep your&nbsp;<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Attack_surface\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">attack surface</a>&nbsp;to a minimum</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Make sure you&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.owasp.org/index.php/Fail_securely\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">fail securely</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Use&nbsp;<a href=\"https://buildsecurityin.us-cert.gov/bsi/articles/knowledge/principles/347-BSI.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">defence in depth</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Adhere to the principle of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://buildsecurityin.us-cert.gov/bsi/articles/knowledge/principles/351-BSI.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">least privilege</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Use&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.owasp.org/index.php/Threat_Risk_Modeling\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">threat modelling</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"http://www.cgisecurity.com/owasp/html/ch04s09.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">Compartmentalize</a>&nbsp;- so your system is not all or nothing</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Hiding secrets is hard - and secrets hidden in code won\'t stay secret for long</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Don\'t write your own crypto</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Using crypto doesn\'t mean you\'re secure (attackers will look for a weaker link)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\">Be aware of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/6701\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">buffer overflows</a>&nbsp;and how to protect against them</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\">There are some excellent books and articles online about making your applications secure:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"http://rads.stackoverflow.com/amzn/click/0735617228\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Writing Secure Code 2nd Edition</strong></a>&nbsp;- I think every programmer should read this</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"http://rads.stackoverflow.com/amzn/click/020172152X\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">Building Secure Software: How to Avoid Security Problems the Right Way</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"http://rads.stackoverflow.com/amzn/click/0596003943\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 89, 153);\">Secure Programming Cookbook</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/viewer?url=http://www.usenix.org/events/sec04/tech/slides/mcgraw.pdf\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; fon