(1, 1, 'About', 'Exam Paper Discussion Platform - EPDP', '<p>Knowledge gathering using discussion is the best efficient way among the</p>\r\n<p>students. In present most of the undergraduate students rely on the internet for</p>\r\n<p>gathering information. However, the main problem of current search features is</p>\r\n<p>university students are unable to answer the questions and discuss the past</p>\r\n<p>examination papers by using uploaded PDF&nbsp;file.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Examination Paper Discussion Platform (EPDP) was created by students of faculty</p>\r\n<p>of Information technology, University of Moratuwa. The system provides user to</p>\r\n<p>a capability of uploading past examination papers as PDF&nbsp;file and answering</p>\r\n<p>questions using pdf files. Our product is mainly focused on past examination paper</p>\r\n<p>discussion among university students as well as the friendliness of the application,</p>\r\n<p>concept of the application, responding speed of the application, user interactivity of</p>\r\n<p>the system, accuracy level of the results, business model for the software.</p>', 'pages/January2018/simple-lamp-wallpaper-53975-55707-hd-wallpapers.jpg', 'about', 'Yar Meta Description', 'Keyword1, Keyword2', 'ACTIVE', '2017-10-24 09:18:28', '2018-01-31 09:34:27');

