(21, 1, 11, 'What should every programmer know about security?', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial,;\">I am an IT student and I am now in the 3rd year in university. Until now we\'ve been studing a lot of subjects related to computers in general (programming, algorithms, computer architecture, maths, etc).</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial,;\">I am very sure that nobody can learn every thing about security but sure there is a \"minimum\" knowledge every programmer or IT student should know about it and my question is what is this minimum knowledge?</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial,;\">Can you suggest some e-books or courses or anything can help to start with this road?</p>', NULL, 'posts/default.jpg', 'what-should-every-programmer-know-about-security-', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2018-01-31 22:03:18', '2018-01-31 22:06:59'),
(22, 1, 13, 'Computer Architecture pipeline stalls', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\">First of all, sorry for my poor English. The question is an problem in my textbook of Computer Architecture course, I\'ve found the answer on the net but still cannot find out the details.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\">The following is a phase of instructions in a five-stage (fetch, decode, execute, memory, write) single-pipeline microarchitecture&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">without forwarding</strong>&nbsp;mechanism.&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">All operations are one cycle except LW and SW are 1 + 2, and Branch is 1 + 1.</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><br></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\">And I have several questions as following.</p><ol style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\">Why the 2nd instruction can start D in C2? As I have leaned, D-stage including \"register read\", but the previous instruction write back to R3 until C7.</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\">Similar to previous one, what is the reasons cause 3rd inst\'s D start at C7, and E start at C11?</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\">Why 4th inst must start at C7 instead of C4?</p></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\">This problem origin from the book \"Computer Architecture : A Quantitative Approach 5e\", example 3.11.</p>', '<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">', 'posts/default.jpg', 'computer-architecture-pipeline-stallswtmWfKxZdTN6EzvNRR6U31oP3', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2018-01-31 22:05:20', '2018-01-31 22:05:20'),
(23, 1, 10, 'What is the difference between Computer Architecture and Computer Organisation?', NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Is there any difference between the terms(or subjects) Computer Architecture and Computer Organization? If yes, what is it? Please Explain me in detail. These two seem to be quite similar fields. Tell them apart by quoting good sources</span><br></p>', NULL, 'posts/default.jpg', 'what-is-the-difference-between-computer-architecture-and-computer-organisationA3SjDHb5oA6pv37Llycc7Dt62', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2018-01-31 22:06:06', '2018-01-31 22:06:06');

